  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hardware-level isolation using Firecracker microVMs",
    "Sub-second VM boot times with minimal overhead",
    "Python-native SDK with context manager support",
    "Automatic networking with NAT and port forwarding",
    "Custom Debian-based rootfs image building",
    "Cross-platform support (Linux/Firecracker, macOS/QEMU)"
